{"tid":506451,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"諗咗幾年 終於諗通呢個韓國漫畫嘅真正意思","createTime":"2017-12-22T08:24:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-09T03:11:27.000Z","uid":152123,"like":336,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"743cce424f1d5d64502e1acde6b29d0792b471b4","tid":506451,"uid":152123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:24:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images4.wikia.nocookie.net/__cb20100504150661/evchk/images/8/8d/Comicwth.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages4.wikia.nocookie.net%2F__cb20100504150661%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F8%2F8d%2FComicwth.jpg&h=36ac6d11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n灰面=將會跳樓嘅人<br />\n最尾個灰面呀爸偷個仔肉丸食<br />\n即係因為唔夠飽 連個仔嘅食物都要偷<br />\n代表家庭財政出現咗問題<br />\n估計係呀爸係經濟支柱 所以老婆仔女都唔知<br />\n仲想瞞騙個仔會買遊戲機比佢補償<br />\n肉丸都要搶嚟食嘅時候 又點可能買到遊戲機呢？<br />\n而最後一幕講隻會推人自殺嘅紅色怪物出現<br />\n代表呀爸即將跳樓 所以佢搶食都代表佢想食飽啲安心上路"},{"pid":"9b71a2095321348cda70c34edb95e4dcd46fce4c","tid":506451,"uid":116530,"like":46,"dislike":6,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:25:44.000Z","msg":"紅色怪物隻眼顏色有咩意思"},{"pid":"b4489af7491954d105d4b8f1a37aa5c96cb5f850","tid":506451,"uid":152123,"like":87,"dislike":25,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紅色怪物隻眼顏色有咩意思</blockquote><br />\n待機狀態<br />\n準備推人=綠色 推人個下=橙色"},{"pid":"5543aff18b9fef79528053bb936f0bae69fa0e16","tid":506451,"uid":152123,"like":22,"dislike":94,"score":-72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:27:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>紅色怪物隻眼顏色有咩意思</blockquote><br />\n待機狀態<br />\n準備推人=綠色 推人個下=橙色</blockquote><br />\n屌睇漏咗 我自膠<br />\n推男人係綠色<br />\n推女人係橙色"},{"pid":"b4d7876fb0223edeb1bc2873ef61551ceb748044","tid":506451,"uid":91633,"like":61,"dislike":2,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T08:28:01.000Z","msg":"又黎世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5d49b4021f0c5a5fe9061efa3fedcbacaae74db","tid":506451,"uid":152123,"like":9,"dislike":12,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-